    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯 Raiffeisen 银行客户为普京的战争机器提供物资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/russia-unit-of-austria-s-raiffeisen-bank-has-clients-supplying-putin-s-military</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据彭博社看到的文件显示，随着俄罗斯军队在乌克兰的不断推进，总部位于维也纳的奥匈帝国莱比锡国际银行一直从为普京的军队提供供货的公司那里赚钱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/russia-unit-of-austria-s-raiffeisen-bank-has-clients-supplying-putin-s-military</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 09:01:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行行长维勒鲁瓦称美国关税令人担忧，增加不确定性</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/ecb-s-villeroy-says-us-tariffs-are-worrying-raise-uncertainty</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国央行行长弗朗索瓦·维勒鲁瓦·德加洛表示，美国总统唐纳德·特朗普对加拿大和墨西哥征收的关税“令人担忧”，并加剧了欧洲的经济不确定性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/ecb-s-villeroy-says-us-tariffs-are-worrying-raise-uncertainty</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 08:22:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>希腊总理呼吁欧盟设立 1000 亿欧元国防基金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/greek-premier-calls-for-a-100-billion-eu-fund-for-defense</link>
      <description><![CDATA[希腊总理基里亚科斯·米佐塔基斯呼吁欧盟共同拨出至少 1000 亿欧元（1020 亿美元）用于防务，加入越来越多希望欧盟对自身安全承担更多责任的国家的行列。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/greek-premier-calls-for-a-100-billion-eu-fund-for-defense</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 07:33:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普誓言惩罚南非的征用法</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/trump-pledges-to-cut-aid-to-south-africa-over-land-expropriation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普表示，由于南非的新土地征用法，美国将停止未来对南非的所有资助。兰特下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/trump-pledges-to-cut-aid-to-south-africa-over-land-expropriation</guid>
